These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Hobby   | chess | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
City: boston, nizza
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| City   | nizza | boston |

 #################################

 
